ng couple travels to a remote island to eat at an exclusive restaurant where the chef has prepared a lavish menu, with some shocking surprises.","genre_ids":[35,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.5924,"vote_count":5929,"poster_path":"/fPtUgMcLIboqlTlPrq0bQpKK8eq.jpg","release_date":"2022-11-17","vote_average":7.168,"backdrop_path":"/4vSBj7BYsyuKCx96EJzGyp20WfY.jpg","original_title":"The Menu","original_language":"en"},{"id":51876,"adult":false,"title":"Limitless","video":false,"overview":"The life of an unsuccessful writer is transformed by a top-secret 'smart drug' that allows him to use 100% of his brain and become a perfect version of himself. His enhanced abilities soon attract shadowy forces that threaten his new life.","genre_ids":[53,9648,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.2086,"vote_count":11275,"poster_path":"/kCokPP4WCQRrrAuZ7FcpIyHr8b2.jpg","release_date":"2011-03-17","vote_average":7.194,"backdrop_path":"/9V6Yq2ZVUmyAPcPyDcCBPnkluKF.jpg","original_title":"Limitless","original_language":"en"},{"id":65,"adult":false,"title":"8 Mile","video":false,"overview":"For Jimmy Smith, Jr., life is a daily fight just to keep hope alive. Feeding his dreams in Detroit's vibrant music scene, Jimmy wages an extraordinary personal struggle to find his own voice - and earn a place in a world where rhymes rule, legends are born and every moment… is another chance.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.7894,"vote_count":7690,"poster_path":"/7BmQj8qE1FLuLTf7Xjf9sdIHzoa.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-08","vote_average":7.14,"backdrop_path":"/jNG7pl0DkN1nzxnbZj4MCGf2VEG.jpg","original_title":"8 Mile","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":313219,"adult":false,"title":"Grasshopper","video":false,"overview":"Movie contains the stories of three people: Suzuki (Toma Ikuta), Kujira (Tadanobu Asano) and Semi (Ryosuke Yamada).  Suzuki is a former middle school teacher. His girlfriend was killed, which led him to quit his job and attempt to take revenge on her murderer. To do so, Suzuki has to infiltrate the underground world of criminals. Kujira is a contract killer for hire. He makes his targets fall into confusion and eventually commit suicide. Semi is a contract killer who uses the knife to take out his targets.","genre_ids":[80,53,28,18],"popularity":0.6663,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/h9YkeTwcSnep0ZvEA6U5KtqCzb5.jpg","release_date":"2015-11-07","vote_average":5.933,"backdrop_path":"/44L1vTmftGyK0aRtKFJMAMHsEc4.jpg","original_title":"グラスホッパー","original_language":"ja"},{"id":48677,"adult":false,"title":"Cloak & Dagger","video":false,"overview":"Davey Osborne is an average 11-year-old boy with an overactive imagination. He spends his days playing video games and pretending to be a spy with his imaginary father-figure, Jack Flack - a substitute for his real father, who is struggling with the recent death of Davey's mother. However, fantasy becomes reality for Davey after he witnesses the murder of an FBI agent, who in his dying breath, gives Davey a mysterious video game cartridge called Cloak & Dagger, which in actuality contains top-secret government information. With the help of his younger friend Kim, the tech savvy Morris, and even a little help from his fictional secret agent mentor, Davey must stay one step ahead of pursuers as he tries to survive a real-life game of espionage in the streets of San Antonio, Texas.","genre_ids":[12,28,10751],"popularity":0.7618,"vote_count":155,"poster_path":"/b7jSCsjZccAwj4nrGXj8XPRAcAc.jpg","release_date":"1984-06-01","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/eF765MoTYrRiXSda5xHVXrFeeQm.jpg","original_title":"Cloak & Dagger","original_language":"en"},{"id":48691,"adult":false,"title":"Goodbye Uncle Tom","video":false,"overview":"Two documentary filmmakers go back in time to the pre-Civil War American South, to film the slave trade.","genre_ids":[18,80,27],"popularity":1.4479,"vote_count":70,"poster_path":"/nLw410E9rnJw13kufNgOtjiGvGk.jpg","release_date":"197